com.logtracking.lib.api.config

Class LogConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.logtracking.lib.api.config.LogConfiguration

  • public final class LogConfiguration
extends java.lang.Object
    Class representing global configuration of logging, creating and formatting issue reports,strategies of crash handling, etc. Object of LogConfiguration is immutable and it cannot be instantiated directly - use LogConfiguration.LogConfigurationBuilder to create and configure of object of configuration.
